{"tid":1394460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[稍長文]有關政治中立","createTime":"2019-08-01T12:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T16:07:00.000Z","uid":143987,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"89300b2a8f154eec5da6906c73bfd72085c9adeb","tid":1394460,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:01:34.000Z","msg":"雖然之前有人解釋過咩係政治中立  <br />\n<br />\n係要係民主民選社會先用到  基於有好多唔同政黨  執政者嘅政黨好可能同其中嘅公務員唔同<br />\n而個啲公務員有可能因為咁而改變工作態度  所以政治中立應該係即使政治取態不同  <br />\n亦唔會應響到平時工作(如本身好勤力變左政權都唔會hea做)<br />\n<br />\n而是次公務員集會同嚟緊好大機會搞嘅罷工 都只係表達訴求嘅一種途徑  亦都係公務員嘅權利<br />\n當中highlight部份 說明公務員罷工嘅合理性<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vPHqm6N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvPHqm6N.jpg&h=027fd120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FLvSMCe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFLvSMCe.jpg&h=f589a2f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oNDkVvz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoNDkVvz.jpg&h=822f4ee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/info/files/panel060314c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csb.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Finfo%2Ffiles%2Fpanel060314c.pdf&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=439fb9bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/info/files/panel060314c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我啱啱同家父講政治中立<br />\n佢話而家政府同紅媒(CCTVB、東方)講到唔撐政府就唔係政治中立  如果唔係我解釋  佢係唔會明哩樣野<br />\n<br />\n講真我之前都係唔識咩係政治中立  以為唔可以有政治立場<br />\n係去到有個巴打出POST解釋過我先明<br />\n<br />\n因此我希望大家  可以透過唔同途徑去同其他人講解下咩叫政治中立<br />\n比佢地知道公務員集會，罷工係佢地嘅權利  <br />\n從而比佢地知道  我地全部人都可以參與  一齊罷工<br />\n<br />\n我哩個解釋係好片面  如果有更好嘅解釋  請各位指出<br />\n<br />\n<code>五大訴求 缺一不可 八月五日 我要罷工</code>"},{"pid":"59aa97e406a1b29e138f6964f67b2a32ae677d4e","tid":1394460,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:01:44.000Z","msg":"<code>五大訴求 缺一不可 八月五日 我要罷工</code>"},{"pid":"3cc45b7906563b55ceb6a516625d7867e73dd948","tid":1394460,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:02:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"040b7cf532d9274c71c775aa538f10158b34a800","tid":1394460,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:09:51.000Z","msg":"<code>五大訴求 缺一不可 八月五日 我要罷工</code>"},{"pid":"b56adf6d7be6643fc55869c3193599f247e65aa1","tid":1394460,"uid":258956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:10:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"329adbaf5ec70d73d087ef2062f573aa43a6228f","tid":1394460,"uid":194894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:11:01.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r1XhJnt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr1XhJnt.png&h=1c8ef63e&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港需要你<br />\n我地都係香港人，我願意罷工</span></span>"},{"pid":"ee30ed20219a3746ac00a5a34354222e719b9ae1","tid":1394460,"uid":258956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:11:10.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可 八月五日 我要罷工"},{"pid":"25bf30b11fef8283142ca86bedda78f851499eed","tid":1394460,"uid":265662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:11:35.000Z","msg":"沒有公義，沒有中立。"},{"pid":"164739dc7fe660f8f744b2a895d8bf0769c74bc4","tid":1394460,"uid":136431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:12:41.000Z","msg":"一個專制政權搬憲政民主嘅理論出嚟，真係貽笑大方"},{"pid":"70114a2e2730adbd2552e3ef8b659c931dec4f80","tid":1394460,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89300b2a8f154eec5da6906c73bfd72085c9adeb","tid":1394460,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:01:34.000Z","msg":"雖然之前有人解釋過咩係政治中立  <br />\n<br />\n係要係民主民選社會先用到  基於有好多唔同政黨  執政者嘅政黨好可能同其中嘅公務員唔同<br />\n而個啲公務員有可能因為咁而改變工作態度  所以政治中立應該係即使政治取態不同  <br />\n亦唔會應響到平時工作(如本身好勤力變左政權都唔會hea做)<br />\n<br />\n而是次公務員集會同嚟緊好大機會搞嘅罷工 都只係表達訴求嘅一種途徑  亦都係公務員嘅權利<br />\n當中highlight部份 說明公務員罷工嘅合理性<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vPHqm6N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvPHqm6N.jpg&h=027fd120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FLvSMCe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFLvSMCe.jpg&h=f589a2f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oNDkVvz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoNDkVvz.jpg&h=822f4ee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/info/files/panel060314c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csb.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Finfo%2Ffiles%2Fpanel060314c.pdf&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=439fb9bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/info/files/panel060314c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我啱啱同家父講政治中立<br />\n佢話而家政府同紅媒(CCTVB、東方)講到唔撐政府就唔係政治中立  如果唔係我解釋  佢係唔會明哩樣野<br />\n<br />\n講真我之前都係唔識咩係政治中立  以為唔可以有政治立場<br />\n係去到有個巴打出POST解釋過我先明<br />\n<br />\n因此我希望大家  可以透過唔同途徑去同其他人講解下咩叫政治中立<br />\n比佢地知道公務員集會，罷工係佢地嘅權利  <br />\n從而比佢地知道  我地全部人都可以參與  一齊罷工<br />\n<br />\n我哩個解釋係好片面  如果有更好嘅解釋  請各位指出<br />\n<br />\n<code>五大訴求 缺一不可 八月五日 我要罷工</code>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:13:03.000Z","msg":"你冇做錯"},{"pid":"18924c562eea6d954d6e352c027222844d7c0143","tid":1394460,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:14:03.000Z","msg":"<code>五大訴求 缺一不可 八月五日 我要罷工</code>"},{"pid":"f9f86cb966d3c7fd72165e8f8f52e4300d6c47c9","tid":1394460,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:21:24.000Z","msg":"<code>五大訴求 缺一不可 八月五日 我要罷工</code>"},{"pid":"24361dde782901b5a33222aa4aee31eda5ba5d31","tid":1394460,"uid":279616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:21:51.000Z","msg":"推比公務員知，參與罷工並不屬於紀律問題，如果高層秋後算帳就係高層政治審查，咁無論你罷唔罷工，根本都會比針對，所以唔洗擔心<br />\n<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與8月5日全港三罷<br />\n#七區集會<br />\n#直至政府跪低"},{"pid":"ffbb35059a72dc18132799c49eed897c14120fad","tid":1394460,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24361dde782901b5a33222aa4aee31eda5ba5d31","tid":1394460,"uid":279616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:21:51.000Z","msg":"推比公務員知，參與罷工並不屬於紀律問題，如果高層秋後算帳就係高層政治審查，咁無論你罷唔罷工，根本都會比針對，所以唔洗擔心<br />\n<br />\n#罷工罷巿罷課<br />\n#我係香港人<br />\n#我參與8月5日全港三罷<br />\n#七區集會<br />\n#直至政府跪低"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:26:29.000Z","msg":"<code>五大訴求 缺一不可 八月五日 我要罷工</code>"},{"pid":"261b83a1122879ab89d8714e792ce0e24294fb38","tid":1394460,"uid":103353,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"89300b2a8f154eec5da6906c73bfd72085c9adeb","tid":1394460,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T12:01:34.000Z","msg":"雖然之前有人解釋過咩係政治中立  <br />\n<br />\n係要係民主民選社會先用到  基於有好多唔同政黨  執政者嘅政黨好可能同其中嘅公務員唔同<br />\n而個啲公務員有可能因為咁而改變工作態度  所以政治中立應該係即使政治取態不同  <br />\n亦唔會應響到平時工作(如本身好勤力變左政權都唔會hea做)<br />\n<br />\n而是次公務員集會同嚟緊好大機會搞嘅罷工 都只係表達訴求嘅一種途徑  亦都係公務員嘅權利<br />\n當中highlight部份 說明公務員罷工嘅合理性<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vPHqm6N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvPHqm6N.jpg&h=027fd120&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FLvSMCe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFLvSMCe.jpg&h=f589a2f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oNDkVvz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoNDkVvz.jpg&h=822f4ee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/info/files/panel060314c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csb.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Finfo%2Ffiles%2Fpanel060314c.pdf&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=439fb9bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/info/files/panel060314c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我啱啱同家父講政治中立<br />\n佢話而家政府同紅媒(CCTVB、東方)講到唔撐政府就唔係政治中立  如果唔係我解釋  佢係唔會明哩樣野<br />\n<br />\n講真我之前都係唔識咩係政治中立  以為唔可以有政治立場<br />\n係去到有個巴打出POST解釋過我先明<br />\n<br />\n因此我希望大家  可以透過唔同途徑去同其他人講解下咩叫政治中立<br />\n比佢地知道公務員集會，罷工係佢地嘅權利  <br />\n從而比佢地知道  我地全部人都可以參與  一齊罷工<br />\n<br />\n我哩個解釋係好片面  如果有更好嘅解釋  請各位指出<br />\n<br />\n<code>五大訴求 缺一不可 八月五日 我要罷工</code>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:01:28.000Z","msg":"我啱啱同家父講政治中立<br />\n佢話而家政府同紅媒(CCTVB、東方)講到唔撐政府就唔係政治中立 如果唔係我解釋 佢係唔會明哩樣野<br />\n<br />\n冇錯<br />\n<br />\n對面最鍾意就係將正面既字詞<br />\n改成對自己有利既意義<br />\n<br />\n我見得最多既係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">法治</span>"},{"pid":"d7925ce294b762ababe9a265825e887473ea89cc","tid":1394460,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:04:14.000Z","msg":"法治都係<br />\n明明法治係用o黎制衡政府  變左做淨係管治市民<br />\n根本錯晒"},{"pid":"4ac76f026e272e2244bbc7a986c540fdc674557c","tid":1394460,"uid":136431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7925ce294b762ababe9a265825e887473ea89cc","tid":1394460,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:04:14.000Z","msg":"法治都係<br />\n明明法治係用o黎制衡政府  變左做淨係管治市民<br />\n根本錯晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:07:05.000Z","msg":"喺大陸佬眼中只有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">法制</span><br />\n兩個字同音"},{"pid":"1db816935bae99fcdfb824c62c405e0da286eefb","tid":1394460,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:55:48.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">五大訴求 缺一不可 八月五日 我要罷工</code></pre>"},{"pid":"570b121bebf340d2c793510c259c98abf3633d79","tid":1394460,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:56:54.000Z","msg":"全民8月5日大罷工！五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年之前落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民黑衫、口罩同頭盔，返工返學行街，唔擺工既日子一齊做，將抗爭帶入生活，保護示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379839</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年之前！"},{"pid":"5f35f8a2d4df581008d3a74a8f4622ae0c42efae","tid":1394460,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3GhazHa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3GhazHa.jpg&h=65930521&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e24905236fe487a2d3a9862a41064fc5d00e4d7d","tid":1394460,"uid":5258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:57:53.000Z","msg":"有無另一位巴打嘅post?想睇"},{"pid":"e426b02df2366b7c26e5dea3a34e8359a24cb791","tid":1394460,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:59:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sno85Pp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsno85Pp.png&h=d28f3c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XRd5oA7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXRd5oA7.png&h=41c349a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5GnqPv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5GnqPv.png&h=072adfbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f8183cf3f6ccfd0d69f1cbf5c569eec6827257d","tid":1394460,"uid":143987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e24905236fe487a2d3a9862a41064fc5d00e4d7d","tid":1394460,"uid":5258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:57:53.000Z","msg":"有無另一位巴打嘅post?想睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:00:09.000Z","msg":"好耐之前  有成大半個月  好難搵<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">五大訴求 缺一不可 八月五日 我要罷工</code></pre>"},{"pid":"d5c0f68eeb4f5ea939a17b2f6242876fed4e98ce","tid":1394460,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:00:25.000Z","msg":"關於自稱「政治中立」人士嘅心理，可以參考呢條片，有詳盡分析，好好睇，強烈建議大家去睇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2cMQAIp9kjU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2cMQAIp9kjU&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEfTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=92b4e712\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2cMQAIp9kjU</a>"},{"pid":"1689e8f27ed7e0b31ca91e00326d4b22a911fa86","tid":1394460,"uid":258362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:07:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1395073/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1395073/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n尋晚反應非常熱烈，今晚繼續"}]}